{
  "stem": "3012.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But her favorite pastime was to have the prisoner-- and it was a women camp, only women, the men were in a different camp-- kneel on the pebbles-- like pebbles like this, that was separating the two rows of barracks in the camp-- holding two pieces of heavy brick like this, and kneeling and holding it until they collapsed.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, for nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or for-- I mean, what can you do wrong in Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything, and nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot recall that she personally beat up somebody with her two hands, or the other woman, Ria.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember ever having seen it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They probably sort of, somehow like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't recall any physical abuse by their own hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I might be wrong, again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then there was a Rapportschreibereien who came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Her name was-- the kapo was Rita, R-I-T-A.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Rapportschreibereien was Ria, R-I-A.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rapportschreibereien, they said, was the woman who drew up the lists of how many prisoners, something like this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something to do with administration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, well-dressed and very clean and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, once in a while, we saw Mengele coming and followed by a woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A young woman in a white smock, carrying a huge, like, a case for sketches, drawings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the latrine news-- because that's where you picked up the rumor from the various people-- had it that she is a Jewish Polish prisoner by the name of Hannah Lazarovich and allegedly Mengele's assistant, who is doing the drawings on his research.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some research, as it turned out later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that allegedly she is his mistress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never read about this, I never heard it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Auschwitz from the 15th of June till the very beginning of August, 1944.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
